# write-stories — job stories

## When to invoke

The user wants JTBD-style job stories: situation, motivation, outcome.

## Steps

1. Use the form: **When** [situation], **I want to** [motivation], **so I can** [outcome].
2. Add acceptance criteria tied to observable outcomes.
3. Link to discovery evidence (interviews, metrics) when available.
4. Save where the team tracks backlog.
